Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.12,0:00:16.98,EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I won’t forget the kindness.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.28,0:00:23.80,EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}It’s always there, even after goodbyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.52,0:00:31.47,EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I try to remember things that feel familiar,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.30,0:00:39.22,EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Counting all the things I don’t yet know.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.70,0:00:51.53,EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}If I could speak to you just as I am, without holding back,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.92,0:01:02.21,EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Only a warm melody would fall upon this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.68,0:01:16.40,EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}The two of us at night, the scent of morning,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.72,0:01:25.38,EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Groping for each other with blurred vision,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.63,0:01:36.18,EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}We nearly reach each other, but then hold our breath.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.53,0:01:43.11,EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I’ve walked this path, knocking on the door of dawn,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.79,0:01:52.71,EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Hoping not to end up like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.55,0:02:08.02,EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}The fragments we shared—I'll give you the larger piece.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.01,0:02:15.82,EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}And yes, I really do like the sweet cream.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.35,0:02:25.37,EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Gently, I lower the needle onto the record in the night,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.37,0:02:31.10,EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Waiting for you until the lonely news arrives.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.41,0:02:41.31,EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Yes, I was waiting for you. Yes, I was waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.53,0:03:09.27,EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}The two of us at night, the scent of morning,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.55,0:03:18.20,EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Reaching out with beautiful hands, feeling our way through,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.51,0:03:28.99,EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Unable to speak well, because we’re holding our breath,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.41,0:03:37.66,EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}As if morning might never come to this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.63,0:03:50.64,EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I’ve walked this path, knocking on the door of dawn, hoping not to end up like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.93,0:04:34.46,EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Imagine, for example, that the two of us were fallen angels,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.02,0:04:41.34,EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Forgetting even where we came from.
